                    This action is permanent. Deleting the <span class="font-bold text-on-surface">Mumbai Main Branch</span> will immediately revoke access for 3 admins and 1,248 students. All associated data will be archived.
                </p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<button class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border border-outline text-on-surface font-title-md hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors" onclick="toggleModal('deleteModal')">Cancel</button>
